<li><strong>Thermal layers:</strong> Merino wool or synthetic base layers, insulating mid-layer, and a windproof outer shell</li>
<li><strong>Warm hat, gloves, and neck gaiter:</strong> The canyon creates a wind tunnel effect that makes it feel colder than ambient temperature</li>
