</ul>

<p>Explore more Banff experiences — browse <a href="https://www.getyourguide.com/banff-l284/?partner_id=QW960HO" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">tours and activities in Banff</a> on GetYourGuide.</p>

<div class="tip-box"><strong>Pro Tip:</strong> The best coffee experience in the Canadian Rockies is at the Lake Agnes Tea House — but it requires a 3.4 km hike to get there. Order a pot of their loose-leaf tea or a hot coffee, sit on the outdoor patio overlooking Lake Agnes, and feel the deep satisfaction of having earned every sip. No drive-through can compete with that.</div>
