<li><strong>Excessive formal wear:</strong> Banff is casual. Even nice restaurants welcome smart-casual attire</li>
<li><strong>Bear spray from home:</strong> You can't fly with it. Buy it in Banff and dispose of it before your flight home</li>
</ul>

<div class="tip-box"><strong>Packing Tip:</strong> Layer, layer, layer. A sunny morning hike can turn into a cold, windy summit. Dress in a moisture-wicking base, insulating mid-layer, and waterproof outer shell — add or remove layers as conditions change. This system works year-round in the Rockies.</div>
