  'spray-river-trail': `
<p>The Spray River Loop is one of Banff's most accessible and scenic trails — a gentle, flat path that follows the Spray River through forests and meadows, past the iconic Fairmont Banff Springs Hotel, and along some of the most beautiful riverside scenery in the park. It's perfect for an easy walk, casual bike ride, or winter cross-country ski, and you can start right from downtown Banff.</p>

