<li><strong>Rogers Pass:</strong> Through Glacier National Park. Towering peaks, avalanche sheds, and historic railway engineering</li>
<li><strong>Three Valley Gap:</strong> A narrow pass with a lake reflecting the mountains</li>
<li><strong>Fraser Canyon:</strong> The highway follows the Fraser River through a dramatic canyon. Stop at Hells Gate for a gondola ride over the churning rapids</li>
<li><strong>The transition:</strong> Watch the landscape change from Rocky Mountain peaks to interior desert to lush coastal rainforest</li>
