<div class="tip-box"><strong>Picnic Tip:</strong> Cascade Ponds is the best all-round picnic spot for families with fire pits and facilities. For romance, Vermilion Lakes at sunset with a blanket and a bottle of wine can't be beaten. Always store food properly — this is bear country.</div>
