  'banff-toddler-guide': `
<p>Let's be honest — visiting Banff with toddlers is a different experience than the Instagram version. You're not summiting mountains or catching sunrise at Moraine Lake. But Banff with little ones can be genuinely wonderful if you adjust your expectations and plan around their rhythms. Here's what actually works.</p>

